Now I need to check if `BinaryData.ToObjectFromJson<T>` has an overload that takes a `JsonTypeInfo<T>`:```csharp// In .NET, BinaryData has:
public T ToObjectFromJson<T>(JsonSerializerOptions? options = default)
// And in newer versions:
public T ToObjectFromJson<T>(JsonTypeInfo<T> jsonTypeInfo)
```

